{"_path":"/blog/2-my-vscode-setup","_dir":"blog","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"My VSCode Setup | Blog","description":"Explore my minimalist VSCode setup featuring the Minimal Mist theme and settings for a clean, distraction-free coding environment.","headline":"My VSCode Setup","abstract":"Discover how the Minimal Mist theme and custom VSCode settings create a clean and focused coding environment.","date":"2024-07-17T12:00:00","dateUpdated":"","author":"Muhammad Ubaid Raza","authorUrl":"/","socialImage":{"src":"/img/blog/2-my-vscode-setup/typescript-dark.png","mime":"png","alt":"Workplace Screenshot","width":1200,"height":630},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"my-vscode-setup"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"My VSCode Setup"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hello, fellow developers! I’m Muhammad Ubaid Raza, and I want to share my latest VSCode setup with you. I've crafted this environment to be as minimalist and distraction-free as possible, and I call it Minimal Mist. This theme and setup have greatly enhanced my coding experience, and I hope it can do the same for you."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"features-of-minimal-mist"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Features of Minimal Mist"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"subtle-background"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Subtle Background"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I chose a soft and soothing background color "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#f6f5f0"}]},{"type":"text","value":". This subtle hue reduces eye strain and creates a calm coding environment, perfect for long coding sessions."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"shadow-free-design"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Shadow-Free Design"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"chi